      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo represents a peerless example of the A80 chassis, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six. The factory sequential induction system delivers linear power across the rev range, mated to a crisp Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission. This specimen remains in an unmolested state, retaining its original helical limited-slip differential and aluminum double-wishbone suspension for precise lateral dynamics. Mechanical tolerances are within factory specifications, ensuring peak volumetric efficiency and structural rigidity. A true investment-grade vehicle for the discerning collector.",
